// Predator-prey classic Lotka-Volterra model
// Volterra V (1928) Variations and fluctuations of the
//   number of individuals in animals species living together.
//   Journal du Conseil 3: 3-51.
// This model is essentially the same as S1987_B1_lotka_volterra.
// The original model is already in canonical S-system form. 
// Recasting should not change anything substantive. 

model Lotka_Volterra()
X = 1; Y = 1
a = 1.1; b = 0.4; c = 0.1; d = 0.4
X' = a*X - b*X*Y
Y' = c*X*Y - d*Y
end
// @SIM T_START=0 T_END=20 N_STEPS=400 